        "synopsis": {
            "value": "Crown Prince Yi Gun (Suho) finds himself in trouble when he is kidnapped by a woman named Choi Myung-Yoon (Hong Ye-Ji). Her father, Royal Physician Choi Sang-Rok (Kim Ju-Hun), brokered an agreement with the royal family to have her selected as the Crown Princess, but her father learns through a fortune teller that his daughter will bring catastrophe and become a widow. To avoid the widow's fate for his daughter, Choi Sang-Rok arranges a bossom (kidnapping) that is meant to ward off such bad fortune. Meanwhile, Crown Prince Yi Gun witnesses a shocking scene inside the royal palace between  the Queen Dowager (Myung Se-Bin) and a man he could only see from behind. To find out the identity of the man he saw, he sneaks out of the royal palace at night. Through fate, Crown Prince Yi Gun is mistakenly kidnapped.",
            "source": "asianwiki",
            "source_link": "https://asianwiki.com/Missing_Crown_Prince"
        },
